  // ── PRIORITY RETENTION CONCEPTS (v7.5.0 seed, 8 entries, additive forever) ─
  // Eight concepts seeded from the public Microsoft AI-900 Skills Measured
  // doc (effective 2025-05-02 — the GenAI/Azure AI Foundry refresh) +
